\section{Product description }
\frame{
\begin{Huge}Product description \end{Huge}}
\subsection{Description}
\frame{\frametitle{Description}
\begin{itemize}
\item The goal of our project is to create two graphical interfaces, 
\begin{itemize}
\item the first will control the parameter of the two transmitter antennas 
\item the second interface will control the two antennas of receiving end.
\end{itemize}
\item The first interface contains certain information, which is:
\begin{itemize}
\item  the channel on which the data will be transmitted 
\item the type of the transmitted data (Picture, Sound, Video)..
\item The stream data rate
\item The carrier frequency
\end{itemize}
\item The second interface contains these informations :
\begin{itemize}
\item the bit error rate (BER)
\item the received data (Picture, Sound, Video)
\item the Peak Signal to Noise Ratio (PSNR)
\item the channel frequency response
\end{itemize}
\end{itemize}
}

