\section{Conclusion}
\frame{
The user requirement is essential before starting any project necessary to be presented to our client. It protects the project developer if the client demands other thing from what we have agreed. Moreover, it gives us an early information of what is the outcome of the project, how will the project will be done, and a brief information on the technology that we will use in our project. It also allows us to propose a solution for the task given under some constraints; time, finance, limited resources.  And finally, it gives us an opportunity of working as a team.}
